  "summaries": [
    "<b>Exploding Bullet</b> is a <linked>Hardmode</linked> <linked>bullet</linked>. It is one of six types of craftable bullets made from <linked>Empty Bullets</linked>, which are sold by the <linked>Arms Dealer</linked> in <linked>Hardmode</linked>. The Exploding Bullet detonates upon contact with an <linked>enemy</linked> or terrain, causing area of effect damage and <linked>knockback</linked> to all enemies caught within the blast radius, even through walls.",
